Inbred Credits Title: Inbred Directed by: Alex Chandon Written by: Alex Chandon; Paul Shrimpton Music by: Dave Andrews Cinematography: Ollie Downey Edited by: Oliver Griffin Production Distributors: New Flesh Films

Split Second Films Released: August 29th, 2011 Rating: R Running time: 90 min. Country: United Kingdom Language: English Navigation Previous: — Next: —

Inbred is an independent British horror film of the psycho-thriller and comedy genres, with an emphasis on violence, and sadism. It was written and directed by Alex Chandon and produced by New Flesh Films and Split Second Films. It was first screened at the Film4 FrightFest on August 29th, 2011. It opened to limited theatrical release in the United Kingdom on October 8th, 2012.
